TextArea_GetCursorPosition
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<TextGadgets=>textgadgets/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<textarea_get_cursor_position>
Syntax:	TextArea_GetCursorPosition
#indent

On entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 0x4018 + 12 (16420)
r3 = gadget component Id
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r4 = cursor index
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method gets the cursor position within a text area (requires TextGadgets 0.22).